e":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"花生<br />\n但我連台灣定大陸品牌 都未識分......<br />\n媽, 我好亂丫~"},{"pid":"a3af8c75888acae75ef23edbd6a5cccfec430235","tid":1421363,"uid":293056,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5899fb298f75d6ff6b8bc228893c3b6a4712297b","tid":1421363,"uid":61724,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"其實人地都出左聲明啦 <br />\n你咁把炮唔掉晒屋企中國制造d野先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:05:32.000Z","msg":"聲明代表啲咩？<br />\n代表繼續奶鞋底咋<br />\n有冇睇清楚 佢自己都識講台灣同大陸代理係同一個人<br />\n所以講到尾咪又係怕無左個經營權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9608c22c20a166993ecc3bbd9be0875fc5eb1be9","tid":1421363,"uid":293056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"9d644d41c87fac7241396583cabe6b8677c34c7c","tid":1421363,"uid":245864,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7492f49cab4a01e440ca92947b3bfcd930bce855","tid":1421363,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHGrLky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHGrLky.png&h=867158fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"台灣加盟店都誤會左以為篇微博聲明係香港代理出<br />\n點知原來係大陸代理（即係台灣總公司老闆）出<br />\n其實你諗下都知有邊春個香港人會用微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港店同台灣加盟店都俾人擺撚左上枱！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港店係同路人！不分化不割蓆！<br />\n噴撚左人地招牌油同我去道歉！<br />\n再幫手同身邊既人講番成件事！<br />\n錯就要認！唔可以抹黑人地！"},{"pid":"3284144f035c85779a5bd80e0c7de11db50ff0ab","tid":1421363,"uid":102243,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"6月12日人地都罷左工<br />\n你同我割蓆？<br />\n果個聲明出係微博<br />\n邊個香港人睇呀<br />\n老虎堂老闆咁仆街你唔搞 去搞一芳<br />\n真係多謝哂"},{"pid":"a10676dbd08e918c50ab2b2472e29dd8b5aa8a5c","tid":1421363,"uid":293056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:22:53.000Z","msg":"如果唔係為左盤生意既會係咩原因？<br />\n咩比人擺上枱丫 根本就係為左盤生意繼續有得做落去又唔想得失啲客咋<br />\n真正支持罷工既係其他特許經營店而唔係兩間直營店丫"},{"pid":"da131dfc63af609f3a090ed548c051f0df1cd3fd","tid":1421363,"uid":153192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"有時間推左即時資訊同戰略po先<br />\n清算po可以容後再出"}]}